{"tid":1805722,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於最近聯署嘅賽後檢討","createTime":"2019-12-31T18:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T19:20:37.000Z","uid":211565,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7486e7aec0b4a570a672a407ae81c59dbec9739b","tid":1805722,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"根據手足呢幾日嘅回應發現‬<br />\n‪其實有部份人唔係唔願意簽‬<br />\n‪而係接觸唔到呢個資訊‬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n‪1.時間太倉猝+宣傳不足‬<br />\n‪-&gt;收到相關資訊先自己<span style=\"color: red;\">檢查下內容有冇伏</span><br />\n    然後就投稿到聯署gp<br />\n    <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=33865e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg</a><br />\n<br />\n -&gt;另外，希望大家入gp同定期c睇下有冇新聯署。我估其實靠gp入邊既人數，其實係可以輕而易舉咁搞掂件事，但似乎好多人都冇留意check gp。<br />\n<br />\n-&gt;亦可以聯絡fb/ig大page睇吓肯唔肯幫手宣傳<br />\n    <span style=\"color: pink;\">但有啲太濫既聯署就算啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n‪另外，亦有部份手足表示不滿所以唔想簽：<br />\n<br />\n‪1.唔知同上一個有咩分別‬，以為一樣所以冇理⋯<br />\n‪-&gt;一句簡單講返上一個係咩 然後(已完成)‬<br />\n‪-&gt;詳細介紹返最新嗰個‬<br />\n    <span style=\"color: pink;\">但其實呢一點我覺得大家已經有改善</span><br />\n<br />\n‪2.‬有咩用呀？<br />\n-&gt;個人認為德國聯署同所羅門叫大家簽嘅聯署都有一定作用。不過兄弟爬山各自努力，唔需要強行說服佢既。與其同佢嘈，不如教多兩個人簽啦？<br />\n<br />\n暫時淨係諗到咁多，大家有諗法歡迎補充。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5412d257dd9ac2c2239e4a06de6c4b38bc3bfe66","tid":1805722,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己推推"},{"pid":"b4078cd95f7a1d86569ecdaec0867f6dbf41c29c","tid":1805722,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:56:53.000Z","msg":"如果大家認同嘅都可以share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3937105e18771d2f6e4aa5edc9864c9c36770d6b","tid":1805722,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"大家覺得「聯署撚」有咩可以改善嘅地方？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eHyHpT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eHyHpT</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署其實同祈禱無分別 (內有建議改善方法)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eHEcaT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eHEcaT</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係睇#1，最好睇埋樓主嘅頭一兩頁嘅留言。"},{"pid":"e7e5c1ee949a1087af598b3f8b566965336d89a8","tid":1805722,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"無可否認,有好多人包括我都有種感覺就係,簽左半年都好似無咩實質作用"},{"pid":"68b3e9f868b8ce9582e910144f3a2b7507df40ae","tid":1805722,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:58:43.000Z","msg":"推多兩推聽日起身先再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305c3bf94b098b4e8b0730ea2d350ed68c1058e1","tid":1805722,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3937105e18771d2f6e4aa5edc9864c9c36770d6b","tid":1805722,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"大家覺得「聯署撚」有咩可以改善嘅地方？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eHyHpT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eHyHpT</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署其實同祈禱無分別 (內有建議改善方法)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eHEcaT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eHEcaT</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係睇#1，最好睇埋樓主嘅頭一兩頁嘅留言。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:59:33.000Z","msg":"咦咦咦已經有人開左 好 我睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1df1d5a9cfd4e7656880b86698c794e0283197","tid":1805722,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7e5c1ee949a1087af598b3f8b566965336d89a8","tid":1805722,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"無可否認,有好多人包括我都有種感覺就係,簽左半年都好似無咩實質作用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:00:08.000Z","msg":"重要或者比較關心議題先會有議員或者官員拎上手討論"},{"pid":"6347a4f66e44664b49335